    "title": "Tx database size (blkindex.dat)",
    "body": "I'm asking myself and repeat a question I read on the forums, what happens if a nodes blkindex.dat grows larger than what we allow for blk000x.dat or (if that size-limit doesn't matter here) larger that the max FAT32 filesize (4 G(i)B - 1 Byte AFAIK)?\n\nSeems like \"blkindex.dat\" is also hard-coded in some places. Comments / ideas?\n",
